When Ms. Meder looked through the crumbling windows of the red-white-and-yellow Art Nouveau building, she saw weeds growing massively between the tiles.
On the other hand, they faced extinction in a magical swimming pool in the Black Forest: the Palais Thermal in Bad Wildbad.
