Since its careful modernization in 1995, the Palais Thermal has been a favorite spa spot for pool expert Mrs. Iris Meder, and not just because it comes from the Black Forest.
&quot;It&#39;s quite a feat to combine such diverse building styles into such a wonderful complex,&quot; says Ms. Meder.
For such a palace, immersion in the thermal pool is apparently a marginal matter.
