A few meters away was the body of another person dressed in a red sports T-shirt and blue cotton pants.
All three were lying face down.
According to the data obtained at the locations, all three persons were probably murdered at another location, as no bullets were found.
Messages addressed from one organized crime group to another were found on the fence of the cottage, as well as numerous bullet marks, both on the building and on the door.
